"{\"uid\": \"thenews.com.pk-latest-1217803-eva-mendes-ryan-gosling-blend-into-crowd-at-olympics-with-their-daughters\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Eva Mendes and her partner Ryan Gosling supported the athletes at the women's gymnastics uneven bars final during the 2024 Olympics in Paris on August 4.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eva_Mendes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eva Mendes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eva_Mendes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eva_Mendes\"}, {\"begin\": 27, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Gosling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Gosling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Gosling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Gosling\"}, {\"begin\": 135, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999969569672, \"rank\": 3.043032606199571e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The couple, accompanied by their daughters Esmeralda (9) and Amada (8), blended into the crowd, with Mendes expressing relief that her children remained out of the spotlight.\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 198, \"end\": 207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chilean_corvette_Esmeralda\", \"score\": 0.9238215375815787, \"rank\": 0.07899919067362288, \"text\": \"Esmeralda\", \"types\": [\"Q11446\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chilean_corvette_Esmeralda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chilean_corvette_Esmeralda\"}, {\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amada\", \"score\": 0.9999998780037987, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amada\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love @nbcolympics did not cut away to the kids !,\\\" Eva wrote in an Instagram comment to a fan Aug. 6.\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.621608652774968e-13, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And most sites blurred their faces so mama bear is happy about that.\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyway it felt so good to be there and feel unified with people.\\\"\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also replied to another commenter, adding, \\\"they were great about not posing the kids so l'm a grateful mama bear.\\\"\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eva Mendes, 50, and Ryan Gosling, 43, have maintained a private relationship and family life since meeting on the set ofThe Place Beyond the Pinesin 2012.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 694, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eva_Mendes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eva Mendes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eva_Mendes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eva_Mendes\"}, {\"begin\": 714, \"end\": 726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Gosling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Gosling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Gosling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Gosling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was during the filming of this movie that Ryan Gosling realised the depth of his feelings for Eva Mendes, marking the beginning of their romantic connection.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 895, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Gosling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Gosling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Gosling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Gosling\"}, {\"begin\": 947, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eva_Mendes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eva Mendes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eva_Mendes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eva_Mendes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't thinking about kids before I met her, but after I met Eva, I realized that I just did not want to have kids without her,\\\" theFall Guyactor toldGQin 2023.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And there were moments onThe Place Beyond the Pineswhere we were pretending to be a family, and I did not really want it to be pretend anymore.\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I realized that this would be a life I would be really lucky to have.\\\"\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1392, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The News International, All Rights Reserved\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1412, \"end\": 1434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_News_International\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The News International\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_News_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_News_International\"}]}]}"